<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 - Internal Server Error</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #333;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .error-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 6rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .error-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .error-description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .error-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            text-align: left;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .back-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .back-button:hover {
            background: #2980b9;
        }
        .timestamp {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #95a5a6;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <h1 class="error-code">500</h1>
        <h2 class="error-title">Internal Server Error</h2>
        <p class="error-description">
            We're sorry, but something went wrong on our end. Our team has been notified and is working to fix the issue.
        </p>
        
        {% if error_message %}
        <div class="error-details">
            <strong>Error Details:</strong><br>
            {{ error_message | escape }}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        
        {% if request_id %}
        <div class="error-details">
            <strong>Request ID:</strong> {{ request_id | escape }}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        
        <a href="/" class="back-button">← Back to Home</a>
        
        <div class="timestamp">
            Error occurred at: {{ "now" | date: "%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S UTC" }}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>